{"tid":432683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英維權人士被拒入境   入境處職員含淚：「我只在執行職務，我不能評論。」","createTime":"2017-10-11T17:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T00:10:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"52c1cb14b45ce5ebed9637cca73520e33ddd6eda","tid":432683,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cry-33_C0lRJ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcry-33_C0lRJ_1200x0.png&h=21df2254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國維權人士、保守黨人權委員會羅哲斯 (Benedict Rogers) ，擬來港拜訪本地的政治人物，結果今午（11日）入境香港時被拒。羅哲斯接受英國《衛報》訪問時指，當他被押送離境時，問到入境處職員一國兩制是否已死，對方含淚拒評。<br />\n<br />\n羅哲斯向《衛報》提到，入境處職員沒有解釋為何拒絕他入境，並指此事非常奇怪（absolutely bizarre）。羅哲斯稱早前已收到警告，有可能被拒入境；儘管已有心理準備，但對此事仍令感到驚訝，沒想到警告成真。他感到這是又一例子，顯示一國兩制名存實亡。<br />\n<br />\n入境處職員押送羅哲斯上機，登機前一刻羅哲斯回頭問了入境處職員一句：「這是否代表一國兩制已死？現在是否已是一國一制？」<br />\n<br />\n羅哲斯憶述，該入境處職員聽聞後，顯得非常悲傷、雙目幾乎含淚地看著他答道：「我只在執行職務，我不能評論。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，入境處回應《立場新聞》查詢時指，有關人員沒有聽過羅哲斯發表有關一國兩制的言論。<br />\n<br />\n羅哲斯又對事件以及香港的情況表示傷感。他曾於 1997 至 2002年期間居於香港，是次他以私人身份來港，希望探望朋友，包括部份著名的政治活躍人士。由英國及多倫多港人組成的「文政網」透露，羅哲斯是次訪港是打算探望黃之鋒、周永康、羅冠聰等在囚抗爭者，及其他政治人物。<br />\n<br />\n「如果一個英國公民只是以私人身份來港探望朋友而被拒入境，這是香港非常令人悲傷的一天。」<br />\n<br />\n雙學三子被判囚後，羅哲斯曾聯同一班居英港人，往英國外交部抗議三子被判監、香港法治及基本自由受破壞，以及英方沉默處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/英維權人士被拒入境-問一國兩制是否已死-稱入境處職員含淚拒評/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%8B%B1%E7%B6%AD%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E5%95%8F%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB-%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%90%AB%E6%B7%9A%E6%8B%92%E8%A9%95%2F&d=CkoTydT07GA4d35S6NBSJJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=179830f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%8B%B1%E7%B6%AD%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E5%95%8F%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB-%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%90%AB%E6%B7%9A%E6%8B%92%E8%A9%95%2F&h=533c6aab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/英維權人士被拒入境-問一國兩制是否已死-稱入境處職員含淚拒評/</a>"},{"pid":"4699a969eb55ec5d91430b4cc2e67929e4282f7c","tid":432683,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T18:52:37.000Z","msg":"又搵食啫"},{"pid":"652144ea13cddc6505b28aed5420a1b8eb566384","tid":432683,"uid":112000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T19:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfc66403ffe70e1c2d36e7687cd404b2220473d","tid":432683,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T19:37:29.000Z","msg":"Mr Johnson said he would seek an &quot;urgent explanation&quot; from the Hong Kong authorities and the Chinese government.<br />\nMr Rogers told Reuters he was not given a reason for being denied entry and was escorted on a flight back to Bangkok.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-41586529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-41586529&d=CkoTydT07GA4d35S6NBSJJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5a3b7839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-41586529</a>"},{"pid":"a0ea902fbf070d4a09c01b7c0bb0dfb4d0e082b7","tid":432683,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T22:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a555bb54092c218dccbd958066146073f4c01c43","tid":432683,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T23:05:01.000Z","msg":"職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ef87ad945691a58549dcd6313d4dd074995d17","ti