:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:02:45.000Z","msg":"屌報復啦英國，連遣責聲明都唔撚發<br />\n屌你老母咁撚鵪鶉對住大陸"},{"pid":"06afe07a71470fb4e50b7b63002382c8aac0842f","tid":432683,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:02:59.000Z","msg":"個職員根本冇講過，又係度作故事分化我哋中國人"},{"pid":"9c96aa1c4d64702533417a5878bdd4dc3f3a6b7b","tid":432683,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌報復啦英國，連遣責聲明都唔撚發<br />\n屌你老母咁撚鵪鶉對住大陸</blockquote><br />\n哇巴撚閉囉，你要去我屋企，我唔俾你入仲報復我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你估而家仲係一八七幾啊？洗唔洗俾埋治外法權你啊？"},{"pid":"f184c6c2e42b2d382ad3eccd8874023fd0d59019","tid":432683,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌報復啦英國，連遣責聲明都唔撚發<br />\n屌你老母咁撚鵪鶉對住大陸</blockquote><br />\n香港人都要搵 入境處 同 政府 問下究竟發生乜嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8247428c35d7ad71edfccf388953d7d112f512","tid":432683,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:10:36.000Z","msg":"鳩up啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一問即刻含淚有冇咁撚誇張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}